Smart3 PHP Framework install instructions
---------------------------------------------

Put the whole package somewhere under the document root folder.
Point your browser to admin.php. You should see an install page.

After successfull setup you are forwarded to the login page. 
You can login with username: "superuser", the password created
during the install and the right captcha number.

You can fill the database with the whole documentation which you
can find in /sql/smart3.sql
Start phpMyAdmin and execute this sql file in the smart3 install database.
Make shure that you havent change the install db table prefixe "smart_"
